{"tid":499573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[盲腸?] 中共話中英聯合聲明失效","createTime":"2017-12-15T03:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-15T11:33:40.000Z","uid":71770,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"92156ce8c95630f67b691252a37bab14c86d9a59","tid":499573,"uid":71770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:28:21.000Z","msg":"1984年12月19日簽訂中英聯合聲明中<span style=\"color: red;\">並沒有聲明廢除此條約，而是<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聲明</span>香港地區（即香港島、九龍及新界）是中國領土</span>，联合王国政府于1997年7月1日将香港交还给中华人民共和国，中华人民共和国政府决定于1997年7月1日对香港恢复行使主权[2]。<br />\n<br />\n咁中共話中英聯合聲明失效, 係咪即係中共自己認香港唔係中國領土?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9284b5f42fd1103e289e273c6f90b3fb184c3d6d","tid":499573,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:51:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7fa467bcbf3538fbdb73dc1f09db368e103067e","tid":499573,"uid":142888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T03:55:54.000Z","msg":"呢單好耐啦，不過冇人理"},{"pid":"cc68d7618e4bf737a15bd87296577c7e6e787b19","tid":499573,"uid":11798,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:30:53.000Z","msg":"咪on9拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港一直都系中國嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2cd1409d37f1adfe72553a3cfda7e73053ad284","tid":499573,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-15T05:35:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪on9拉<img src=\"/asse